      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Abdullah Bin Muhammad, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hisham Bin Salim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The impatient false oath leaves the houses deserted’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "6. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from ‘Abd Allah ibn Muhammad from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hisham ibn Salim who has narrated the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘A binding oath which is false leaves the town barren.’” "
        ]
      }
